Package: scrippsWorkflowPlotting
Type: Package
Title: Scripps Workflow R-side plotting library
Version: 1.1.0
Description: Companion to the Python lib/plotting library. Provides
    ggplot2-based renderers that share theme.json and the figure-id
    catalog so a Python-rendered and R-rendered figure of the same
    figure_id are visually equivalent. Sourced as plain R files from
    runtime/plotting_r/core.R; not built as a CRAN package.
Imports:
    ggplot2 (>= 4.0.0),
    grDevices,
    grid,
    jsonlite,
    ragg,
    scales,
    stats,
    utils
Suggests:
    Cairo,
    cowplot,
    digest,
    ggrepel,
    patchwork,
    RColorBrewer,
    viridisLite
License: see ../../LICENSE
